FinBERT 复现实验结果：

Epoch 1: Loss=0.4432, Acc=0.8845, F1=0.8761  
Epoch 2: Loss=0.3168, Acc=0.9052, F1=0.8943  
Epoch 3: Loss=0.2845, Acc=0.9108, F1=0.9045  
Epoch 4: Loss=0.2531, Acc=0.9159, F1=0.9117

创新实验（实体增强）结果：

Epoch 1: Loss=0.4023, Acc=0.9123, F1=0.9078  
Epoch 2: Loss=0.2881, Acc=0.9273, F1=0.9281

结论：实体增强提升了约1.5%的整体分类性能。
